Implementing the Command Pattern

Scenario:
You are developing a home automation system where commands can be issued to turn devices on or off. Use the Command Pattern to achieve this.

-> Command Pattern turns a request into a stand-alone object.
-> It allow parameterization of clients with different requests, queuing of requests and support of undoable operations.

The practical implementation can be accessed at: Exercise #9/CommandPatternExample/src/command/
